SELECT  levenshtein("test", TRIM(LOWER(scan.lastname))) AS lastname_lev ,  levenshtein("test", TRIM(LOWER(scan.firstname))) AS firstname_lev ,  100-(levenshtein("test", LOWER(scan.lastname))*100/LENGTH(scan.lastname)) AS ratio ,  100-(levenshtein("test", LOWER(scan.firstname))*100/LENGTH(scan.firstname)) AS ratio_rev , scan.*,
          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-01-27 15:02:10") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote,  1 as _is_admin  FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk)))  WHERE 1  AND ( scan.lastname LIKE "%test%" OR  scan.firstname LIKE "%test%" )  GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY  IF(MAX(ratio) >= MAX(ratio_rev), ratio, ratio_rev) DESC , lastname desc, firstname desc, PK desc  LIMIT  0 ,25

SELECT m.*, min(m2.sl_meetingpk) as min_date, pl.status as pl_status, pl.active as pl_active, pl.created_by as pl_created_by, pl.sl_position_linkpk,
        min(pl2.sl_position_linkpk) as min_date_position, pl.positionfk as positionfk, slc._sys_status as candidate_status
        ,pl.date_completed , pl.date_created as ccm_create_date
        FROM sl_meeting m
        INNER JOIN sl_candidate slc on slc.sl_candidatepk = m.candidatefk AND slc._sys_status = 0
        INNER JOIN sl_meeting m2 ON m2.candidatefk = m.candidatefk
        INNER JOIN sl_position_link pl ON pl.candidatefk = m.candidatefk
        INNER JOIN sl_position_link pl2 ON pl2.positionfk = pl.positionfk
        WHERE pl.date_completed >= "2017-01-01 00:00:00"
        AND pl.date_completed <= "2017-01-31 23:59:59"
        AND pl.status = 51
        AND pl.active = 0
        AND pl2.status = 51
        AND pl2.active = 0
         
        AND slc._sys_status = 0
        group by pl.candidatefk, pl.positionfk
        order by m.candidatefk

            , TIMEDIFF("2017-01-27 16:46:49", noti.date_notification) as d
            FROM notification as noti INNER JOIN notification_action as nact ON (nact.notificationfk = noti.notificationpk) LEFT JOIN notification_recipient as nrec ON (nrec.notificationfk = noti.notificationpk) LEFT JOIN notification_link as nlin ON (nlin.notificationfk = noti.notificationpk AND linked_to = 'item') LEFT JOIN shared_login as slog ON (slog.loginpk = nrec.loginfk) WHERE noti.type IN ("reminder", "email")  AND noti.delivered < 1  AND nrec.loginfk = 343  AND noti.date_notification >= "2017-01-27"  AND noti.date_notification <= "2017-01-29"  GROUP BY noti.notificationpk ORDER BY noti.date_notification DESC  LIMIT 0, 10

SELECT * FROM `login` l
      LEFT JOIN login_group_member lm ON l.loginpk=lm.loginfk  WHERE 1  ORDER BY l.firstname, l.lastname
1sec - start: 2017-01-30 05:41:03 / end: 2017-01-30 05:41:04
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

SELECT m.*, min(m2.sl_meetingpk) as min_date, pl.status as pl_status, pl.active as pl_active, pl.created_by as pl_created_by, pl.sl_position_linkpk,
        min(pl2.sl_position_linkpk) as min_date_position, pl.positionfk as positionfk, slc._sys_status as candidate_status
        ,pl.date_completed , pl.date_created as ccm_create_date
        FROM sl_meeting m
        INNER JOIN sl_candidate slc on slc.sl_candidatepk = m.candidatefk AND slc._sys_status = 0
        INNER JOIN sl_meeting m2 ON m2.candidatefk = m.candidatefk
        INNER JOIN sl_position_link pl ON pl.candidatefk = m.candidatefk
        INNER JOIN sl_position_link pl2 ON pl2.positionfk = pl.positionfk
        WHERE pl.date_completed >= "2016-11-01"
        AND pl.date_completed <= "2017-01-31"
        AND pl.status = 51
        AND pl.active = 0
        AND pl2.status = 51
        AND pl2.active = 0
         
        AND slc._sys_status = 0
        group by pl.candidatefk, pl.positionfk
        order by m.candidatefk
1sec - start: 2017-01-30 05:41:07 / end: 2017-01-30 05:41:08
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

      , slp.status, slp.date_completed, slp.date_created as ccm_create_date, slp.active, slp.candidatefk as candidate, slc._sys_status as candidate_status FROM sl_meeting slm INNER JOIN sl_meeting m2 ON m2.candidatefk = slm.candidatefk AND m2.meeting_done = 1 INNER JOIN sl_position_link slp on slp.candidatefk = slm.candidatefk  INNER JOIN sl_candidate slc on slc.sl_candidatepk = slp.candidatefk WHERE slm.created_by IN (371)

      GROUP BY slp.sl_position_linkpk ORDER BY ccm_create_date DESC

SELECT count(DISTINCT scan.sl_candidatepk) as nCount FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk) ) AND ( elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_type = "candi" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  INNER JOIN event as even ON (( even.eventpk = elin.eventfk AND even.type NOT IN ('cp_hidden', 'cp_history') ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  WHERE 1   and ( even.content  LIKE  "%haccp%" )

SELECT scan.*,
          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-01-30 13:48:01") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote,  1 as _is_admin  FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk) ) AND ( elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_type = "candi" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  INNER JOIN event as even ON (( even.eventpk = elin.eventfk AND even.type NOT IN ('cp_hidden', 'cp_history') ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  WHERE 1   and ( even.content  LIKE  "%haccp%" ) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY TRIM(scan.lastname) ASC, TRIM(scan.firstname) ASC  LIMIT  0 ,25

SELECT scan.*,
          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-01-31 14:57:42") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote,  1 as _is_admin  FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk) ) AND ( elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_type = "candi" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  INNER JOIN event as even ON (( even.eventpk = elin.eventfk AND even.type NOT IN ('cp_hidden', 'cp_history') ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  WHERE 1   and ( even.content  LIKE  "%test%" ) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY TRIM(scan.lastname) ASC, TRIM(scan.firstname) ASC  LIMIT  0 ,25
